Foreword
It was a war that broke out at the beginning of the new year around every ordinary, ordinary Chinese.
This is our war. We discuss it eagerly, analyze it carefully, deplore the loss of life in the disaster, are moved by the fearless spirit of the healer, and work tirelessly for the little things we can do.
The Sea of life, we walk and cherish.
Netease's "Our war" feature tells the story of how, every day, we meet the epidemic shirtless.

Our war has been going on for 11 years

On the New Year's Day holiday, I woke up naturally, lying in bed, swiping wechat, "On the first day of 2020, Wuhan has become a 'boiling point' , " a media friend in Wuhan posted. "We can never predict tomorrow. It will be safe to wear a mask to regulate emotions, work and rest on time, and take scientific precautions. "
My heart clattered a sound, Internet search, only to see a few pieces of Wuhan pneumonia of unknown Cause News, said to be related to the seafood market.
"Can not be like that year 'SARS' like. " Read the news to my husband, I muttered.
He absent-mindedly sneers at: "earn the money that sells cabbage but fuck sells white powder heart, you save! "
"We're just talking about it at home. Why all the sarcasm? "
He immediately serious up: "again 'sars' I do not have to be afraid. You are in the rear this time, do not have to go straight up? "
Seventeen years ago, during the SARS epidemic, I was a first-line medical nurse. Although our 18th-line small town in the northeastern corner of China did not eventually have a confirmed case of SARS, the jitters of prevention and control are still fresh in my memory. When I was on duty at fever clinic or pre-examination and triage, it was like going to the battlefield, it is not known which patient may be carrying the virus "bomb" . I happened to be on duty when the fever clinic encountered a "suspected case" , according to the requirements of life was isolated for a week, make the family worried, unwilling to eat, sleep hard. I didn't go home to my family until the patient was cleared of suspicion. That roller coaster general mood ups and downs, as if the experience of life and death in general.
Today, I am a "second-line" administrative office of middle-level Leaders, daily attendance morning meetings and leading group meetings, the position is only auxiliary nature, general meetings, I only silence to do minutes.
After work, responsibility, sense control section colleagues in the morning meeting, "Wuhan unexplained pneumonia" , the president instructed them to pay more attention, early prevention.
Shortly before the morning meeting on January 20, when the outbreak in Wuhan was reported to the whole country, vice president ye conveyed the spirit of a teleconference held by the provincial health and Health Commission, calling for the immediate prevention and control of COVID-19 pneumonia. Zhang then deployed the work: Immediately Open Fever Clinic, medical staff out-patient secondary protection, fever patients to do a survey (epidemiological survey) , all medical staff in other departments all wear masks on duty.
The leaders of the administrative departments related to prevention and control, such as the medical department, the nursing department, and the sense control department, recorded the work requirements and immediately carried them out separately. The remaining members of the leading group continued to hold meetings and studied the routine work such as the pre-festival safety inspection, also commented on last Friday's Spring Festival gala, the atmosphere is relaxed and happy.
In the afternoon, the middle-level leaders of the hospital held a regular meeting, emphasizing medical protection, medical safety and fire safety during the festival, as well as epidemic prevention and control. That night, Ye, who had bought his ticket in advance, flew to his son in Dalian for a family reunion. He had been on annual leave for several years, and as a specialist in smoking medicine, he had offered a refund, but the director said, "Go, I'll watch the fever clinic for you. "
No one expected that the situation behind the prevention and control of development so fast.

On January 21, the shift will be changed in the morning, and the General Duty Report at night: the pre-examination triage nurse guided six patients with body temperature higher than 37 degrees 5 to the fever clinic. Two of them refused to wear face masks, and their families also swore, nurse suspects"take off pants fart redundant". The security guards showed up and took them out of the Er and into the fever clinic in the quarantine area.
Dean instructions: "No matter how difficult, but also adhere to the principle of pre-examination and triage, explain to patients, prevention and control work must not be careless, outside loose inside tight, so as not to cause social panic. "
At this time, the atmosphere in the whole hospital was fairly good. The hospital planned to wish the people of the city a happy and healthy Chinese New Year on the wechat account during the Spring Festival. In addition to working in various departments and offices, the hospital was working together and racking its brains to shoot a new year video, some departments also posted Spring Festival couplets ahead of time.
I also went out to the Riverside Square, want to see the unit on display lanterns, as promised by the advertising agency, "Shiny full-court gorgeous pressure fragrance. ". Before I left, I put on the medical mask I had just given out to the field office. The street was full of festive atmosphere, with crowds of people crowding around each other. It was very peaceful and festive. Even if I occasionally saw a few wearing masks, they were also cold-proof. The light blue color on my face was very different.
Out of the door is the pharmacy, I went in, and bought a few more masks, 3m, N95, medical, a bag of the same. I didn't know it was true 20 days ago, but I thought it would be a good idea to stock up on face masks, even to prevent a cold.
In the evening, I and my husband's two relatives in the crowd, advised everyone to wash their hands, more ventilation, less public places, had to wear a mask, the results were few. "Fear not, " said the retired sister-in-law. "excessive panic also lowers the immune system. " Her 70-year-old uncle said in her voice: "It's okay. I didn't wear a mask when I was fighting SARS. We are in the best place in the world. We didn't have any patients when we were fighting SARS, and we won't have any this time. "
My uncle's story is typical, i've also seen some pollyannas in my circle of friends -- as if I weren't going anywhere, just hanging out here! Flood in 1998, we are OK here; SARS in 2003, we are OK here; bird flu in 2006, we are OK here; earthquake in 2008, we are OK here; H7n9 in 2013, we are OK here. There is Paradise in heaven and Suzhou and Hangzhou in heaven. If we avoid disaster, we are the strongest here!"

On the third day of the Lunar New Year, the bad news Life Unexpected: the number of confirmed cases in the province has increased to 21, with one death.
Of course, there is good news: our small city a total of five suspected cases, were finally ruled out, including a visit to the Wuhan people, just ordinary flu.
But a file photo began to go viral on small town people's wechat accounts. It appeared that a certain department had written a description of the situation: a native of Wuhan arrived with his wife and in-laws on New Year's Eve, he has stayed in two hotels and his parents'home, and is now under quarantine in the First Hospital of the city. There's a name, an ID number, an address down to the number of the house. Or how the file got out.
Friends and relatives kept calling me and asking, "has the Wuhan man been diagnosed? "
The Dean and the First Hospital confirmed that the rumor was that the man was the same person who had been released from quarantine for the common cold. He hastened to inform us of the widespread "scrunchies" : This person is not new crown pneumonia, just common cold.
In a few moments, the whole town was buzzing with rumours among its friends.
My hometown also began to close the village. My cousin told everyone not to go back to pay New Year's greetings. "The people of this village are not allowed to enter. " A video of the village chief patrolling the streets with a megaphone was also distributed. As he walked, he called out by the neck: "The mask or the suction machine, you always look at the alternative" , "the UNFILIAL son who takes the disease back to his hometown, infected his parents to be heartless! "
Uncle said: "This is not all posted on the Internet slogan? This boy will learn to use it. "

Two days later, the medical section issued the "hospital personnel health registration form" , asking us to report body temperature before and when leaving the post, filling in the presence or absence of respiratory symptoms. After a few days of overwork, a group of colleagues became sick. The director asked them to stay on duty and rest. He did not encourage them to work with illness. After the vacation from the field back is home quarantine doctors and nurses, not through the epidemic area, the lifting of quarantine early on duty, to replace the fallen.
A colleague laughed and said, "this is called back-to-back... "
I said, even if it is a succession, really more than "SARS" period of science. It was also a tough year for prevention and control, with a shortage of staff, and many doctors and nurses who weren't feeling well or making any noise, who weren't hurt in the line of fire, were in good spirits, but they did raise the risk of infection, thank God there were no confirmed cases.
In the evening, the province has confirmed 37 cases, suspected 87 cases, and there are adjacent cities "occupied" , the province only 4 cities "fruit left. Someone posted a picture of four little people hugging each other in a group of friends, saying, "F4, hold on. Who lets go first? WHO's the puppy? ". But soon, "F4" became the mask-wearing Haier brothers, and one of them was us.
Although we use online channels to warn people who do not have a history of contact with an infected area and have only mild cold symptoms not to come to the doctor to avoid the risk of infection, more and more people are coming to the fever clinic. Some people come in at 37 degrees without any symptoms, others feel feverish at 36 degrees, and panic attacks have brought more than two or three times the usual number of visits.
Just as our protective materials were "bottoming out" and everyone was burning with anxiety, on the evening of the sixth day of the Lunar New Year, a heartening news came from the medical staff: a large quantity of protective materials purchased by the district government from Russia crossed the frozen river, finally made it to our port.

Early in the morning of February 2nd, however, before we read the official news, we saw in the working group that there was a confirmed case at a hospital. "It's true, I've checked with the hospital, " said the Dean in a plaintive voice as the crowd followed President  Department head
The government immediately announced that, on top of the suspension of public transport, taxis were also suspended and large supermarkets were closed for a limited time. For a while, also in the open market, vegetable shops, grain stores, supermarkets there was a rush to buy. Fortunately, small town folk honest, although prices slightly higher than usual, but basically up before the Spring Festival, no merchants take the opportunity to bid up prices.
The government also responded quickly, sending public security police around to inspect the evacuation of the crowd, while issuing a notice through various media to let everyone not panic, "road closure is not closed daily supplies logistics channels, absolutely guarantee the supply of daily life. ". Soon the streets were deserted again.
Prevention and control situation is more and more serious, our hospital has already had 3 suspected patients. Front-line doctors in Shanghai, Wuhan and other places have also released patients with negative nucleic acid test for the first two times, but the third positive clinical experience, we feel nervous. Emergency Meeting of hospital prevention and Control Leading Group to discuss how to "upgrade prevention and control" ———————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————— Also began "three-level protection" , in the original basis, plus wearing a comprehensive type of protective gear.
Obstetrics and gynecology needs to solve the problem is also urgent: Other patients can go online for medical treatment, maternal children can not be isolated at home, and pregnant and lying-in women are precisely the high-risk groups. After a discussion, the delivery room has become a "war zone" , such as the reception of the maternal enemy.
Fortunately, there are always some touching moments, so that the heart of the warm flow dispel the gloomy mood.

Early on the morning of Feb. 3, a masked man walked through the pre-screening triage post at the emergency department, pulled a large bag from his chest, placed it on the nurses'station workbench, and left without a word. When the nurse opened it, she saw at least 200 N95 masks and chased them out, only to see the back of them speeding by. Shortly thereafter, a photo of him appeared in friends'circles as if he had been photographed giving masks away in other hospitals and first line positions.
At noon, another take-out agency and a restaurant sent us 120 free meals, so that the medical staff who worked overtime to satisfy their hunger with instant noodles ate hot rice and drank warm milk tea. They said they would keep feeding us until we got rid of the virus, but the director declined -- as if hospital was the biggest risk for infection -- but they said they weren't.
That night, the government issued a food and beverage, express ban on business announcement, they also regret.
After work in the evening walk on the road, used to be a traffic jam on the street, now very empty. Back in the neighborhood, a group of young volunteers, dressed in blue jackets, walk through the streets of Florida as they spray disinfectant from one building to the next, each carrying a large sprayer.
Watching this scene, I suddenly remembered Percy Bysshe Shelley's famous poem: "Winter is coming, will spring be far away? "

Both the oral and Otolaryngology doctors complained about the lack of goggles in case the patient had an incubation period during tooth extraction and laryngoscopy; the imaging doctors immediately followed the video, learn to make a batch of protective masks: old x-rays cut after the installation of hat brim, can cover most of the face. The lack of goggles was well addressed when these humble items were handed out to the relevant departments.

On the first day of the New Year, I got up early and picked up some food at home. I hurried to the hospital to replenish the protective articles for each post.

The president said: The government is coordinating material support. We are across the river from Russia. Many businessmen engaged in border trade have already extended a helping hand. They are in contact with Russian enterprises. Special arrangements should be made for them. They should soon be able to open ports and come in to protect materials, if there are more suspected cases, must be protected according to the National Sensory Control Standard —— change the isolation suit once on the job, and change the mask once every 4 hours.

The door of the medical section was open, and the young chief of the section was eating a ramen sausage with a camp-bed propped up by his desk.

"Didn't go home? " I called.

"I dare not return. The protocol keeps changing, and I just finished the second edition, which is now the third edition, so I have to get the doctors and nurses on it. The leading groups for prevention and control at the municipal and district levels are also constantly issuing instructions and have to carry them out consistently."

It is normal that there are changes in the diagnosis and treatment plan. All diseases must have a cognitive process. The National Health Commission is organizing experts to constantly revise the diagnosis and treatment plan based on the experience of the front-line treatment. A friend in the friend circle said: "finally know why I was not afraid of SARS that year, there is no WECHAT AH! This open a cell phone, the heart immediately PLOP TACHYCARDIA! " I think, there is some truth in it. We had a suspected case of SARS in our hospital, but before the official news was announced on TV, not to mention ordinary citizens, colleagues outside the relevant departments in the hospital were not very aware of the situation.

The outbreak came in a hurry, the hospital supplies reserve is small, consumption is very large, no one thought that follow-up procurement would be this situation. Both the oral and Otolaryngology doctors complained about the lack of goggles in case the patient had an incubation period during tooth extraction and laryngoscopy; the imaging doctors immediately followed the video, learn to make a batch of protective masks: old x-rays cut after the installation of hat brim, can cover most of the face. The lack of goggles was well addressed when these humble items were handed out to the relevant departments.

Co-workers are pulling together to finish the job, and few take time off.
Early in the morning on the second day of the eighth lunar month, a letter of invitation from each department was sent to the party office. Almost everyone signed their names and pressed their red handprints. The head of the nursing department, who was due to retire on Feb. 1, also submitted a request for a delay in retirement, and many doctors and nurses said they could ride to Wuhan's aid if necessary.
Just as fear can be contagious, so can positive energy.
The director instructed the Medical Department to organize clinical doctors to set up a "Wechat Group of guidance for the diagnosis and treatment of mild cases" , telling the public through the WECHAT PLATFORM: mild cases can be consulted online to obtain treatment plans, if not necessary, do not come to the hospital for treatment, in order to minimize the risk.
Qr Code has just announced to the community, can add 200 places can be used up in an instant, we soon opened two more groups; psychological counseling certificate colleagues, but also actively opened a psychological counseling group.
Such a rapid "online response" was unthinkable during the SARS era.
District Party secretary to inspect the work of prevention and control, the door was "gun" relative. He was not angry, but also gave a thumbs-up: "Well done! " The courtyard leader hurried down the stairs to lead, for him to do a good job, after the depth of "front line" , while reporting to work. Referring to the medical staff's request for war, the secretary said: "Good! Very Times, we need such spiritual strength. "
Just then, my son called me -- as if he were setting up a checkpoint on the border with a neighboring county, more than 100 kilometers from the city. Several departments jointly dispatched cars. The traffic police stopped the passing cars, and disease control officers monitored the passengers'body temperatures, police officers prevent stops from rioting, forest police search for no wildlife, as I answered, my son opened his mouth and said, "mom, you said the district government is so stingy... "
I glanced at the District Party secretary, who was two steps ahead, and he was looking back at me. Then I remembered that the phone was silent, and I hung up in fear. I didn't know if he had heard my son.
My son thought I had a bad signal and changed it to a voice on Wechat. I converted the voice into text and understood what it meant: "That side (referring to the neighboring county) has also set up a card, doing even more absolutely. Cars that are not their license plates will not be allowed to enter. " But the nearest gas station to the checkpoint is 10 kilometers into the next county, and the cars here want to refuel, and there's no way to say otherwise. The boys at the checkpoint had to go to the district government and ask for fuel, only to be criticized as "too expensive" .
"Cold Weather, we do not even mouth hot water, minus 20 degrees, do not bomb the gas pedal into the car to warm for a while, freeze to death? Two cars are dead, people are crowded in the other two cars... " my son's words make me some heartache.
But I ignored my son and hurried to follow the inspection team. The District Party secretary went to the pre-examination and triage post of the inpatient department, went to two departments and fever clinic, praised the medical staff all the way.
As soon as the secretary left, a doctor whispered, "what is he here to examine? "
I glared at him. "It's not an inspection, it's an inspiration! "

On the third day of the Lunar New Year, the bad news Life Unexpected: the number of confirmed cases in the province has increased to 21, with one death.
Of course, there is good news: our small city a total of five suspected cases, were finally ruled out, including a visit to the Wuhan people, just ordinary flu.
But a file photo began to go viral on small town people's wechat accounts. It appeared that a certain department had written a description of the situation: a native of Wuhan arrived with his wife and in-laws on New Year's Eve, he has stayed in two hotels and his parents'home, and is now under quarantine in the First Hospital of the city. There's a name, an ID number, an address down to the number of the house. Or how the file got out.
Friends and relatives kept calling me and asking, "has the Wuhan man been diagnosed? "
The Dean and the First Hospital confirmed that the rumor was that the man was the same person who had been released from quarantine for the common cold. He hastened to inform us of the widespread "scrunchies" : This person is not new crown pneumonia, just common cold.
In a few moments, the whole town was buzzing with rumours among its friends.
My hometown also began to close the village. My cousin told everyone not to go back to pay New Year's greetings. "The people of this village are not allowed to enter. " A video of the village chief patrolling the streets with a megaphone was also distributed. As he walked, he called out by the neck: "The mask or the suction machine, you always look at the alternative" , "the UNFILIAL son who takes the disease back to his hometown, infected his parents to be heartless! "
Uncle said: "This is not all posted on the Internet slogan? This boy will learn to use it. "

Two days later, the medical section issued the "hospital personnel health registration form" , asking us to report body temperature before and when leaving the post, filling in the presence or absence of respiratory symptoms. After a few days of overwork, a group of colleagues became sick. The director asked them to stay on duty and rest. He did not encourage them to work with illness. After the vacation from the field back is home quarantine doctors and nurses, not through the epidemic area, the lifting of quarantine early on duty, to replace the fallen.
A colleague laughed and said, "this is called back-to-back... "
I said, even if it is a succession, really more than "SARS" period of science. It was also a tough year for prevention and control, with a shortage of staff, and many doctors and nurses who weren't feeling well or making any noise, who weren't hurt in the line of fire, were in good spirits, but they did raise the risk of infection, thank God there were no confirmed cases.
In the evening, the province has confirmed 37 cases, suspected 87 cases, and there are adjacent cities "occupied" , the province only 4 cities "fruit left. Someone posted a picture of four little people hugging each other in a group of friends, saying, "F4, hold on. Who lets go first? WHO's the puppy? ". But soon, "F4" became the mask-wearing Haier brothers, and one of them was us.
Although we use online channels to warn people who do not have a history of contact with an infected area and have only mild cold symptoms not to come to the doctor to avoid the risk of infection, more and more people are coming to the fever clinic. Some people come in at 37 degrees without any symptoms, others feel feverish at 36 degrees, and panic attacks have brought more than two or three times the usual number of visits.
Just as our protective materials were "bottoming out" and everyone was burning with anxiety, on the evening of the sixth day of the Lunar New Year, a heartening news came from the medical staff: a large quantity of protective materials purchased by the district government from Russia crossed the frozen river, finally made it to our port.

". Soon the streets were deserted again.

Early on the morning of Feb. 3, a masked man walked through the pre-screening triage post at the emergency department, pulled a large bag from his chest, placed it on the nurses'station workbench, and left without a word. When the nurse opened it, she saw at least 200 N95 masks and chased them out, only to see the back of them speeding by. Shortly thereafter, a photo of him appeared in friends'circles as if he had been photographed giving masks away in other hospitals and first line positions.
At noon, another take-out agency and a restaurant sent us 120 free meals, so that the medical staff who worked overtime to satisfy their hunger with instant noodles ate hot rice and drank warm milk tea. They said they would keep feeding us until we got rid of the virus, but the director declined -- as if hospital was the biggest risk for infection -- but they said they weren't.
That night, the government issued a food and beverage, express ban on business announcement, they also regret.
After work in the evening walk on the road, used to be a traffic jam on the street, now very empty. Back in the neighborhood, a group of young volunteers, dressed in blue jackets, walk through the streets of Florida as they spray disinfectant from one building to the next, each carrying a large sprayer.
Watching this scene, I suddenly remembered Percy Bysshe Shelley's famous poem: "Winter is coming, will spring be far away? "
